---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="About ‚Äì Fragkosyko" description="Discover the story behind our hidden garden restaurant in Naxos, Greece.">
  <Header />

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-warm-sand/30 to-sea-teal/10">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-serif font-bold text-garden-green mb-6">
        Our Story
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg max-w-3xl mx-auto text-charcoal/80">
        A celebration of Naxos, its flavors, and the art of island hospitality
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our Story -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Fragkosyko was born from a love of Naxos‚Äîits sun-soaked mornings, its vibrant evenings,
            and the way life here moves between the energy of the day and the calm of the night.
            We wanted to create a space that captures this rhythm, a hidden garden where locals and
            travelers alike can gather, relax, and savor the island's best.
          </p>

          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Tucked away in the heart of Naxos Town, our courtyard is an oasis‚Äîwhitewashed walls,
            lush greenery, and the kind of light that shifts beautifully from morning to midnight.
            By day, it's the perfect spot for a leisurely brunch and a perfectly brewed coffee.
            By night, the space transforms into an intimate setting for cocktails, conversation,
            and connection.
          </p>

          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
            Every detail, from the seasonal menu to the thoughtfully curated drinks, reflects our
            commitment to celebrating local producers, traditional flavors, and the warm hospitality
            that Naxos is known for. We invite you to step into our garden and experience it for yourself.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Name -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-prickly-pear/10 to-warm-sand/30">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-8 justify-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-prickly-pear/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
            <span class="text-3xl">üåµ</span>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-4xl font-serif font-bold text-garden-green">The Name "Fragkosyko"</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg">
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Fragkosyko (Œ¶œÅŒ±Œ≥Œ∫œåœÉœÖŒ∫Œø) is the Greek word for the prickly pear cactus, a plant deeply
            rooted in the landscape and culture of the Greek islands. Its bright pink fruit and
            resilient nature have made it a symbol of the Mediterranean‚Äîbeautiful, enduring, and
            bursting with flavor.
          </p>

          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
            The prickly pear inspired not only our name but also our visual identity and flavor
            philosophy. You'll see its colors woven throughout our space‚Äîthe soft greens of the
            cactus pads, the vibrant pink of the fruit, and the warm earth tones of the Cycladic
            landscape.
          </p>

          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
            Like the fragkosyko, our restaurant is about thriving in balance‚Äîhonoring tradition
            while embracing the new, offering a welcoming presence in a beautiful, sometimes unexpected place.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our Philosophy -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-cycladic-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-serif font-bold text-center mb-12 text-garden-green">
          Our Philosophy
        </h2>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <!-- Local Ingredients -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-garden-green/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6 mx-auto">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-garden-green" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3.055 11H5a2 2 0 012 2v1a2 2 0 002 2 2 2 0 012 2v2.945M8 3.935V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 0010.5 8h.5a2 2 0 012 2 2 2 0 104 0 2 2 0 012-2h1.064M15 20.488V18a2 2 0 012-2h3.064M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-center mb-4 text-garden-green">Local Ingredients</h3>
            <p class="text-center text-charcoal/80 leading-relaxed">
              We work closely with Naxos farmers, fishermen, and producers to source the freshest,
              highest-quality ingredients. Our menu changes with the seasons to celebrate what's
              growing and thriving on the island.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Slow Mornings -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-sea-teal/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6 mx-auto">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-sea-teal" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-center mb-4 text-sea-teal">Slow Mornings</h3>
            <p class="text-center text-charcoal/80 leading-relaxed">
              Brunch is meant to be savored, not rushed. We create a space where you can linger
              over coffee, enjoy conversation, and ease into the day at your own pace‚Äîthe island way.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Crafted Evenings -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-prickly-pear/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6 mx-auto">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-prickly-pear" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M20 7l-8-4-8 4m16 0l-8 4m8-4v10l-8 4m0-10L4 7m8 4v10M4 7v10l8 4"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-center mb-4 text-prickly-pear">Crafted Evenings</h3>
            <p class="text-center text-charcoal/80 leading-relaxed">
              Our cocktails are made with intention‚Äîseasonal ingredients, local spirits, and herbs
              from our own garden. Each drink tells a story and reflects the flavors of Naxos.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Hospitality-Driven -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-garden-green/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6 mx-auto">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-garden-green" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-center mb-4 text-garden-green">Hospitality-Driven</h3>
            <p class="text-center text-charcoal/80 leading-relaxed">
              Greek hospitality‚Äîphiloxenia‚Äîis at the heart of everything we do. We want every guest
              to feel welcomed, cared for, and at home in our garden, whether it's your first visit
              or your fiftieth.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Team -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-warm-sand/20 to-sea-teal/10">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-serif font-bold text-center mb-4 text-garden-green">
          Meet the Team
        </h2>
        <p class="text-center text-lg text-charcoal/70 mb-12">
          The people behind your garden experience
        </p>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <!-- Team Member 1 -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
            <div class="h-64 overflow-hidden">
              <img src="/team/dimitris_molindris.jpg" alt="Dimitris Molindris" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
            </div>
            <div class="p-6 text-center">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-bold mb-1 text-garden-green">Dimitris Molindris</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-sea-teal font-semibold mb-3">Head Chef</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-charcoal/70">
                Dimitris brings years of culinary experience and a deep love for traditional Greek
                flavors reimagined with a modern touch.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Team Member 2 -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
            <div class="h-64 overflow-hidden">
              <img src="/team/christos_lagios.jpg" alt="Christos Lagios" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
            </div>
            <div class="p-6 text-center">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-bold mb-1 text-garden-green">Christos Lagios</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-sea-teal font-semibold mb-3">Bar Lead</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-charcoal/70">
                Christos crafts cocktails that tell the story of Naxos‚Äîusing local spirits,
                island herbs, and creativity behind every pour.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Team Member 3 -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
            <div class="h-64 bg-gradient-to-br from-warm-sand/30 to-garden-green/10 flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-6xl opacity-20">üë§</span>
            </div>
            <div class="p-6 text-center">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-bold mb-1 text-garden-green">Christos Oikonomou</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-sea-teal font-semibold mb-3">Host & Manager</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-charcoal/70">
                Christos ensures every guest feels at home, bringing warmth, attention to detail,
                and the spirit of Greek hospitality to every table.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Call to Action -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-garden-green text-cycladic-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-serif font-bold mb-6">
        Experience Our Garden
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Join us for brunch, coffee, cocktails, and the warm hospitality of Naxos
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a
          href="/reservations"
          class="px-8 py-3 bg-cycladic-white text-garden-green rounded-full hover:bg-warm-sand transition-all hover:shadow-lg text-lg font-semibold"
        >
          Book a Table
        </a>
        <a
          href="/menu"
          class="px-8 py-3 border-2 border-cycladic-white text-cycladic-white bg-transparent rounded-full hover:bg-cycladic-white/10 transition-all text-lg font-semibold"
        >
          View Menu
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

